/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7c35f0a3d9412c217dfbc51520347b916309d6ca","tid":2211470,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"國民擋到底係咪為台灣人執政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日害台灣人賣台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c0ee3907f730e4a0994e2524260a08fbb906fe","tid":2211470,"uid":219183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c35f0a3d9412c217dfbc51520347b916309d6ca","tid":2211470,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"國民擋到底係咪為台灣人執政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日害台灣人賣台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"人哋支那人嚟<br />\n仲要好自豪嗰隻<br />\n唔好老屈佢哋做台灣人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea2230e1974be13d5e5ae69225c86df57e8f561","tid":2211470,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"人地明明話英文不好, 個個屈佢話英文不好"},{"pid":"09857c85e112ba2cc12b138e5415011bed5255ad","tid":2211470,"uid":253608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c35f0a3d9412c217dfbc51520347b916309d6ca","tid":2211470,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"國民擋到底係咪為台灣人執政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日害台灣人賣台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"國民黨入面係有種寧願比人統都不願被綠執政"},{"pid":"f075cbe660f499eb1aaf9b1b34b12b32f32bf3da","tid":2211470,"uid":256292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92be30605ac4077c0296c930a0184fed1fc0facf","tid":2211470,"uid":335434,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f72c0f5169dad98fbb96fe